  - m_Id: 183701936951399
    m_Localized: SCOUT LODGE  /  EXPEDITION BOARD
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951400
    m_Localized: WHY THE TRAIL MATTERS
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951401
    m_Localized: Scouts range by day and night, reveal unexplored land, investigate
      landmarks, and report distant Iron and Coal deposits - and whatever else waits
      beyond the fog.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951402
    m_Localized: ONE LODGE  /  ONE SCOUT  /  REASSIGN ANY TIME
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951403
    m_Localized: THE FIRST EXPEDITION
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951404
    m_Localized: Beyond the Firelight
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951405
    m_Localized: The roofs are standing and the camps are working, but beyond the
      last familiar path the valley is still only rumor. Choose one adult to carry
      our first map into the unknown.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951406
    m_Localized: APPOINT A SCOUT
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951407
    m_Localized: Choose Who Takes the Trail
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951408
    m_Localized: Every map begins with someone willing to leave the familiar road.
      Choose an adult to carry the Lodge's compass and chart what waits beyond the
      settlement.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951409
    m_Localized: PLAN AN EXPEDITION
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951410
    m_Localized: How Far Beyond the Firelight?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951411
    m_Localized: 'The Scout is ready and the route is open. Choose how many days
      of provisions to pack: a longer expedition can chart more ground, but every
      dawn beyond the Lodge costs another ration.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951412
    m_Localized: Scout or Lodge no longer ready
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951413
    m_Localized: The selected resident is no longer available. Choose another Scout.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951414
    m_Localized: That resident is no longer available for the trail.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951415
    m_Localized: Ready to choose the range of this expedition.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951416
    m_Localized: Ready to carry the settlement's first map.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951417
    m_Localized: Ready to take the Lodge's compass beyond the familiar roads.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951418
    m_Localized: This Scout or Lodge is no longer ready to depart.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951419
    m_Localized: The chosen resident is no longer available. Choose another Scout.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951420
    m_Localized: The expedition cannot leave without all required rations.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951421
    m_Localized: Departure could not be completed. Provisions or the Lodge state
      may have changed.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951422
    m_Localized: No one can leave their duties today. Return when an adult is free.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951423
    m_Localized: The first expedition must wait until enough rations are stored.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 183701936951424
    m_Localized: The selected resident is no longer available for the trail.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
